menu "DIY / Homebrew CPUs"

config ARCH_ZELOOF
bool "Sam Zeloof Homemade CPU Support"
help
  Support for Sam Zeloof's revolutionary homemade CPUs.
  First person to fabricate working silicon in a home garage!

config ZELOOF_Z1
bool "Zeloof Z1 (2018 - First IC)"
depends on ARCH_ZELOOF
help
  Support for Z1 - First homemade integrated circuit with 6 transistors.
  10 micron process, fabricated with DIY lithography equipment.

config ZELOOF_Z2
bool "Zeloof Z2 (2021 - First CPU)"
depends on ARCH_ZELOOF
default y
help
  Support for Z2 - First homemade CPU with 1200 transistors!
  4-bit processor running at ~50 Hz, 10 micron CMOS process.
  Revolutionary achievement in DIY semiconductor fabrication.

config ZELOOF_Z3
bool "Zeloof Z3 (Future - Improved CPU)"
depends on ARCH_ZELOOF
help
  Planned support for Z3 - 8-bit processor with 5000 transistors.

endmenu

